rows.label: tlk41700161_02_msg0001
rows.name:
The Liberalitan Divine Beast's meant to be
hidden somewhere in the Cloud Sea
ridge, but I've never actually seen it.

rows.label: tlk41700161_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I tried navigating Lud Cloudway
myself just to get a peek, but it
didn't go so well.

rows.label: tlk41700161_02_msg0003
rows.name:
The monsters there are tough blighters.
They kept hounding me. I didn't even
get to see a trace of the Divine Beast.

rows.label: tlk41700161_02_msg0004
rows.name:
If you do happen to find it, don't tell
me what it looks like. I want to see it
with my own two eyes.
